---
// Mitra & Relawan CTA section - YPSM Jombang
---

<section class="bg-neutral-50 py-20">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-primary-900 mb-4 font-heading">
      Jadi Mitra Kami
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Ajak perusahaan, masjid, atau komunitas Anda bergandeng tangan untuk pendidikan santri
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Card 1: Donatur Rutin -->
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">&#x1F91D;</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-3 font-heading">
          Donatur Rutin
        </h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-8">
          Donasi bulanan mulai Rp 50.000 untuk santri
        </p>
        <button
          onclick="event.preventDefault();window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('campaign:donate',{detail:{campaign:'general',campaignLabel:'Donasi Rutin'}}))"
          class="bg-coral-500 hover:bg-coral-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all"
        >
          Donasi Rutin
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Mitra & Relawan -->
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">&#x1F49A;</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-3 font-heading">
          Mitra &amp; Relawan
        </h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-8">
          Bergabung sebagai relawan atau mitra program
        </p>
        <a
          href="/kontak/"
          class="inline-block bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all"
        >
          Hubungi Kami
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
